"lúdico e divertido com imagens coloridas."

#: includes/Admin/AdminTranslations.php:125
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Build an elegant site for \"Valley Vista Vineyard,\" offering wine tastings, "
"tours, and bottle sales. Use rich, earthy colors like burgundy, deep green, "
"and cream. Design should feel rustic yet refined with event calendar and "
"wine collection showcase."
